<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<style>/* Reset some default styles */
    body, h1, h2, p, img {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    
    /* Style the header */
    header {
        background-color: #04007C;
        color: #fff;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px 0;
    }
    
    /* Style the container for content and image */
    .container {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        margin: 20px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    
    /* Style the about content */
    .about-content {
        flex-basis: calc(50% - 20px);
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    
    .about-content h2 {
        font-size: 24px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    
    .about-content p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
    }
    
    /* Style the about image */
    .about-image {
        flex-basis: calc(50% - 20px);
    }
    
    .about-image img {
        max-width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        border-radius: 5px;
    }
    
    /* Style the footer */
    footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px 0;
        background-color: #333;
        color: #fff;
    }
    </style>
<body>
    <%- include("partials/nav.ejs") %>
    <%- include("partials/nav2.ejs") %>
    <header>
        <h1>About Us</h1>
    </header>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="about-content">
            <h2>Our Story</h2>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nullam vehicula justo in lectus sollicitudin dignissim.</p>
            <p>Quisque tincidunt ipsum nec urna tristique, at tincidunt nulla scelerisque. Integer tristique ut odio sit amet.</p>
            <p>Suspendisse potenti. Nam vehicula, libero et fringilla imperdiet, leo nulla ullamcorper mi, nec feugiat neque eros.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-image">
            <img src="https://plus.unsplash.com/premium_photo-1661274209157-118069b926f3?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxzZWFyY2h8MXx8dGVhbXxlbnwwfHwwfHx8MA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=60" alt="Our Team">
        </div>
    </div>
    
<%- include("partials/footer.ejs") %>

</body>
</html>
